Matplotlib 2.0 and the Viridis colour scheme¶

  • Viridis is a yellow/blue spectrum
  • "matplotlib 2.0 == matplotlib 1.5 + default style changes"
  • What's new in 1.5? http://matplotlib.org/devdocs/users/whats_new.html
    • Interactive OO usage
    • Working with labeled data like pandas DataFrames
    • New colour maps
